use flake .

# Kakadu FOD in flake.nix uses `gh release download`. Auto-export a
# token if the user is logged into gh; safe no-op otherwise. After the
# first successful CI build, Cachix serves the FOD output by content
# hash and this token becomes unnecessary.
if command -v gh >/dev/null 2>&1 && gh auth status >/dev/null 2>&1; then
  export GH_TOKEN=$(gh auth token)
fi

